      <title>空客重返 1 美元商店，这次与 Spirit 资产达成交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/airbus-returns-to-the-1-shop-this-time-with-spirit-asset-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在几乎免费收购庞巴迪公司陷入困境的 C 系列飞机项目近七年后，空中客车公司再次打折收购 — — 这次是以象征性的 1 美元价格收购 Spirit AeroSystems Inc. 出售的资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/airbus-returns-to-the-1-shop-this-time-with-spirit-asset-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 08:04:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
